                "invention-title": [
                    "Research method for soil water replenishment and earth surface vegetation conditions through phreatic water evaporation and application",
                    "一种潜水蒸发补给土壤水及地表植被情况的研究方法及应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a research method for soil water replenishment and earth surface vegetation conditions through phreatic water evaporation and application of the research method in research of ecological restoration of semi-arid grassland strip mine areas. According to the method, a certain amount of hydrogen and oxygen isotope tracing liquid is injected into the to-be-measured buried depth soil layer to simulate the to-be-measured buried depth phreatic water surface, so that the problems that in an existing field test, phreatic water levels with different buried depths are blindly found, a large number of drill holes need to be drilled, the workload is huge, the field phreatic water depth is fixed, and the testing efficiency is high are solved. The problem that target burial depth diving is not easy to carry out due to the fact that artificial change is difficult is solved, test research is greatly facilitated, the test cost is saved, the hydrogen and oxygen isotope tracing liquid is injected into a burial depth soil layer to be tested through an in-situ test and a plastic hose, the reliability of a test result is high, and the engineering implementation difficulty is small."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种潜水蒸发补给土壤水及地表植被情况的研究方法及其在研究半干旱草原露天矿区生态恢复中的应用。本发明方法通过将一定量的氢氧同位素示踪液注入待测埋深土层以模拟待测埋深的潜水面，避免了现有野外试验中盲目寻找不同埋深的潜水位，需要钻非常多钻孔，工作量巨大及野外潜水埋深一定，人为难以改变从而不容易进行目标埋深潜水影响试验的问题，大大方便了了试验研究、节约了试验成本，且本发明通过原位试验和将氢氧同位素示踪液通过塑料软管注入待测埋深土层，试验结果可信度高、工程实施难度小。"
                }
            ]
